所有已实现的接口：
Flags, Kinds, TypeTags
public class ClassWriter
extends ClassFile
implements Flags, Kinds, TypeTags

This class provides operations to map an internal symbol table graph rooted in a ClassSymbol into a classfile.

字段详细信息

outDir

public java.io.File outDir
Can be reassigned from outside: the output directory. If outDir = null, files are written into same directory as the sources the were generated from.
